"    Severe lichen sclerosus (LS)",
"   </div>",
"   <div class=\"cntnt\" style=\"width: 263px; height: 360px; background-image: url(data:image/jpeg;base64,);\">",
"   </div>",
"   <div class=\"lgnd\">",
"    Long-standing vulvar LS in a 55-year-old lady with severe pruritus for eight years. She woke up most nights scratching. Clitoris is almost buried. The inner labia minora and vulvar trigone are thick, firm and white with two biopsy sites visible on the left side.",
"    <div class=\"footnotes\">",
"    </div>",
"    <div class=\"reference\">",
