"   <div class=\"ttl\">",
"    Lichen sclerosus (LS) adult 45 yrs",
"   </div>",
"   <div class=\"cntnt\" style=\"width: 297px; height: 360px; background-image: url(data:image/jpeg;base64,);\">",
"   </div>",
"   <div class=\"lgnd\">",
"    45-year-old woman with purpura from scratching plus loss of labia minora. The white areas of LS show a cellophane-like shiny surface.",
"    <div class=\"footnotes\">",
"    </div>",
"    <div class=\"reference\">",
"     Reproduced with permission from: F William Danby, MD, FRCPC, FAAD&nbsp;and Lynne J Margesson, MD.",
